Live demo: http://sinatra-seedling.herokuapp.com

A simple Ruby Sinatra powered webapp base project. Uses sinatra-authenticaion & MongoMapper for user login & permissions, and Twitter Bootstrap for styling.

Works out of the box on Heroku.


Set the following environment variables:

A long/tricky cookie secret:
COOKIE_SECRET

Database connection info:
DATABASE_HOST
DATABASE_PORT
DATABASE_PASSWORD
DATABASE_USER
DATABASE

SMTP info:
EMAIL_HOST
EMAIL_USER
EMAIL_PASSWORD

Google analytics ID:
GOOGLE_ANALYTICS
